metadata.name: NEORT Vessel 1
metadata.description:
A collaboration work between NEORT and various artists.
It is a vessel to accept various creativity by artists.
The appearance can be switched to NEORT logo mode and artwork mode by pressing 'c' key.

Artwork(logo): [QmaiDD5gqw17kPbKKP1imRAgofpYSwysh8JKTJNfEkS4En](https://neort.mypinata.cloud/ipfs/QmaiDD5gqw17kPbKKP1imRAgofpYSwysh8JKTJNfEkS4En?seed=1)
